'''安東尼·麥可·拉澤里'''（{{lang-en|Anthony Michael Lazzeri}}，{{bd|1903年|12月6日|1946年|8月6日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的二壘手。生涯曾效力過洋基、小熊、道奇與巨人等隊。他是洋基隊著名的[[殺手打線|殺手打線]]中的一員。

目前拉澤里仍是美聯單場打回最多分打點的紀錄保持人，他在1936年5月24日的比賽中打回11分打點。而他也是大聯盟史上第一位單場敲出兩發滿貫砲的球員。1991年，拉澤里被名人堂資深委員會引薦入選名人堂。
==職業生涯==
拉澤里於1922年於小聯盟開啟職業生涯。1925年，拉澤里寫下職業棒球員單一球季最多的222分打點。<ref name="milb">{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140824&content_id=90959248&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|title=Los Angeles Dodgers prospect Joc Pederson joins Pacific Coast League 30/30 club for Albuquerque Isotopes | MiLB.com News | The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=milb.com|accessdate=2014-09-06|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324230822/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140824&content_id=90959248&vkey=news_milb&fext=.jsp&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>  當時小聯盟已經和小熊隊達成協議，不過基於拉澤里的癲癇病史，小熊最後放棄簽下他。下一順位的紅人隊也宣布放棄，最後由洋基隊成功簽下。<ref name=sabr>{{cite web|first=Fred|last=Glueckstein|url=http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/1b3c179c|title=Tony Lazzeri|publisher={{tsl|en|Society of American Baseball Research||Society of American Baseball Research}}|accessdate=2012-08-28|archive-date=2014-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525201024/http://sabr.org/bioproj/person/1b3c179c|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===紐約洋基===
洋基隊總管Ed Barrow用了Frank Zoeller、Mack Hillis以及5萬美元向小聯盟換來拉澤里。<ref name=sabr/>1926年，拉澤里登上大聯盟。他與另一名新秀Mark Koenig輪流擔任球隊先發二壘手。該年拉澤里全勤出賽，敲出18轟與114分打點。這年洋基隊順利闖進世界大賽，不過鏖戰7場不敵紅雀。其中第七場的7局下，拉澤里在滿壘情況下還遭到宿醉未醒的[[格羅佛·克里夫蘭·亞歷山大|格羅佛·克里夫蘭·亞歷山大]]給三振出局。<ref name=sabr/><ref name=ws1927>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=40sbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=K0sEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1823,2568086&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Pittsburgh Press''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=40sbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=K0sEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1823,2568086&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201116113046 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>

1927年，這年洋基隊組成了可怕的殺手打線。拉澤里這年繳出3成09的打擊率，外帶18轟與102分打點的成績。最後他們在世界大賽上4連勝橫掃海盜。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=k81PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sFQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3075,5517756&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Evening Independent''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=k81PAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sFQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3075,5517756&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201116203342 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>球季結束後，拉澤里一度因為肌肉傷勢差點中止了他的職業生涯，不過他後來仍繼續在場上馳騁。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1D4uAAAAIBAJ&sjid=K9gFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3053,6314289&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Miami News''] via Google News Archive Search</ref>1928年世界大賽，洋基再度與紅雀相遇。這次拉澤里成功從亞歷山大手中敲出關鍵安打，最後洋基再次完成4連勝橫掃。而拉澤里在MVP票選上也拿下第三名。<ref name=colorful>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7UobAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9koEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3196,1865550&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Pittsburgh Press''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7UobAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9koEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3196,1865550&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201116095437 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref><ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=P-BPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pVQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1401,6706152&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Evening Independent''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=P-BPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pVQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1401,6706152&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20220110034313 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1928.shtml#ALmvp|title=1928 Awards Voting|publisher=Baseball-Reference.com|accessdate=2012-08-28|archive-date=2010-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100105031701/http://www.baseball-reference.com/awards/awards_1928.shtml#ALmvp|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1929年，拉澤里繳出生涯新高的3成54打擊率。1932年世界大賽，拉澤里敲出2轟幫助球隊拿下冠軍。1933年，他入選了大聯盟第一屆的明星賽。<ref name=sabr/>不過他在1934年遭遇了膝蓋傷勢。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gkwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=nEsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4920,3040676&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Pittsburgh Press''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gkwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=nEsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4920,3040676&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201121122650 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>

1936年5月24日，他單場敲出11分打點，至今仍是美聯紀錄。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/842945572.html?dids=842945572:842945572&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=May+25%2C+1936&author=&pub=Hartford+Courant&desc=Tony+Lazzeri+Sets+New+American+League+Record+By+Driving+In+11+Runs+For+Yanks&pqatl=google |title=Tony Lazzeri Sets New American League Record By Driving In 11 Runs For Yanks: Hits Three Home Runs And Also Bangs Triple Frank Crosetti Slams Out Two Four-Base Clouts and DiMaggio Drives One Ball Out of Park as New Yorkers Overpower Athletics, 25 to 2|newspaper=The Hartford Courant|page=14|publisher={{tsl|en|Hartford Courant||Hartford Courant}}|agency=Associated Press |date=1936-05-25 |accessdate=2013-09-12}} {{subscription required|date=September 2013}}</ref>同個月，他還在連續4場比賽敲出7發全壘打。1936年世界大賽，拉澤里敲出大聯盟世界大賽史上出現過兩次的滿貫全壘打。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=g_FBAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DaoMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1743,4191055&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Telegraph-Herald''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=g_FBAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DaoMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1743,4191055&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201116201354 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>隔年，他又在世界大賽上跑回致勝分。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JPQzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Ce8HAAAAIBAJ&pg=5256,965992&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''Lodi News-Sentinel''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JPQzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Ce8HAAAAIBAJ&pg=5256,965992&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201117005408 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>

===生涯後期===
1937年球季結束後，洋基隊將拉澤里釋出。<ref name=release>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7yJkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VnsNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1366,5045654&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Calgary Daily Herald''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7yJkAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VnsNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1366,5045654&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20151223114506 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>1938年，小熊隊網羅了拉澤里。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JbNQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RSIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4690,546193&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Milwaukee Journal''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JbNQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RSIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4690,546193&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20151223113700 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>這年小熊隊順利拿下聯盟冠軍，不過卻在世界大賽上被拉澤里的前東家洋基隊橫掃。<ref name=sabr/>1939年，拉澤里加入了道奇隊。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V25IAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Gg0EAAAAIBAJ&pg=1475,1766058&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Milwaukee Sentinel''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=V25IAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Gg0EAAAAIBAJ&pg=1475,1766058&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20151223115032 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>不過他在出賽14場比賽繳出2成82的打擊率後被球隊釋出。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ISohAAAAIBAJ&sjid=V34EAAAAIBAJ&pg=2360,5257132&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Milwaukee Journal''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ISohAAAAIBAJ&sjid=V34EAAAAIBAJ&pg=2360,5257132&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20151223115329 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref><ref name=giants>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=72AtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5tcFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1692,1866040&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Miami News''] via Google News Archive Search</ref>後來他在隔天加入了巨人隊，並擔任球隊三壘手。<ref name=giants/>6月7日，他又遭到球隊釋出。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=jwotAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4tcFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3055,1056052&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Miami News''] via Google News Archive Search</ref>

1938年至1941年，拉澤里都在小聯盟打球。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hGoiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WKsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=7048,567359&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''San Jose News''] {{Wayback|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=hGoiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WKsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=7048,567359&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en |date=20201116071630 }} via Google News Archive Search</ref>1942年與1943年，他在小聯盟同時擔任球員兼總教練。<ref>[https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=cU4aAAAAIBAJ&sjid=_iIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=2386,2327350&dq=tony-lazzeri&hl=en ''The Milwaukee Journal''] via Google News Archive Search</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/871823782.html?dids=871823782:871823782&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=May+01%2C+1943&author=&pub=Hartford+Courant&desc=Tony+Lazzeri+To+Be+Active+With+Barons&pqatl=google|title=Proquest – Courant.com|publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com|date=1943-05-01|accessdate=2012-08-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/courant/access/872927342.html?dids=872927342&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Jan+11%2C+1944&author=&pub=Hartford+Courant&desc=Tony+Lazzeri+Asked+To+Resign+By+General+Manager+Of+Wilkes-Barre+Barons&pqatl=google |title=Proquest – Courant.com |publisher=Pqasb.pqarchiver.com |date=1944-01-11 |accessdate=2012-09-10}}</ref>

