==去世==
1946年，拉澤里因為從樓梯上摔下來去世，享年僅42歲。<ref>[http://www.baseball-almanac.com/deaths/tony_lazzeri_obituary.shtml ''New York Times'' Tony Lazzeri Obituary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/deaths/tony_lazzeri_obituary.shtml |date=20201117024440 }} at www.baseball-almanac.com</ref><ref>[https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&id=2dBcJfBze6sC&dq=Tony+Lazzeri&printsec=frontcover&source=web&ots=BiY6AUV_Dr&sig=R8LAC3umzDumvEzqwwwcm7M_A0M&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=7&ct=result#PPA170,M1 ''Tony Lazzeri'' by Paul Votano] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?hl=en&id=2dBcJfBze6sC&dq=Tony+Lazzeri&printsec=frontcover&source=web&ots=BiY6AUV_Dr&sig=R8LAC3umzDumvEzqwwwcm7M_A0M&sa=X&oi=book_result&resnum=7&ct=result#PPA170,M1 |date=20201122031414 }} at www.googlebooks.com</ref>根據驗屍官的報告，拉澤里因為心臟病發而從樓梯上跌倒。不過後人認為拉澤里應該是癲癇發作而不是心臟病。<ref>[http://entertainment.howstuffworks.com/tony-lazzeri-hof.htm How Stuff Works entry on Tony Lazzeri] {{Wayback|url=http://entertainment.howstuffworks.com/tony-lazzeri-hof.htm |date=20210121024315 }} at entertainment.howstuffworks.com</ref>
